This will be a 3-part dive into the subject of sin as seen throughout the Hebrew Bible and the New Testament.
The beginning seems like as good a place as any to start, so here we go&hellip;
In the Beginning In the first three chapters of the Bible, in the book we call Genesis, we have two creation accounts. The first one is from Genesis 1:1 to the first half of 2:4, and the second one starts in the second half of verse 4 and continues until the end of Chapter 3.
